v4.0
Release date : 09 Jul 2025
-	New weather.sh v4.0
-	New playerctl script
-	Change folder name and script path
-	Some changes in execi command
-	New rings lua script with rounded option
-	Change disk usage bar with lua script { also rounded }
-	Slight theme size changes
-	Added total data that has been downloaded and uploaded
-	Drop support for Mpd version, you can still use mpd but need to install mpdris2 so that it can be read in playerctl
-	Some minor change


v3.0
Release date : 15 Dec 2023
-	Added line draw_blended in conky config due transparent image issue in Gnome & KDE
